### 名词解释

1.  `F-measure`

2.  特征提取`SWT`、`MSER`、`HoG`

3.  `RPN`: Region Proposal Network

4.  [Wolf’s standard](https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Object-count%2Farea-graphs-for-the-evaluation-of-and-Wolf-Jolion/03f8124a4cb74a347735fc0aac0984903d2976e1) 文字框选的标准

5.  Selective Search，R-CNN中使用

6.  Region Proposal Network（RPN），Faster R-CNN

7.  







